{"tid":875214,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"條女成日藍剃 灰剃我","createTime":"2018-10-24T17:50:17.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-24T17:59:08.000Z","uid":218450,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"66db84d2ad14f7c5c4bba735d048b9cd902ba16a","tid":875214,"uid":218450,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-24T17:50:18.000Z","msg":"話說我同條女拍拖<br />\n自從佢去左外國讀書之後<br />\n完全不顧我感受<br />\n利申我係好無安全感<br />\n佢唔係身邊<br />\n我成個人會好低落 好唔開心<br />\n所以想搵佢傾計<br />\n可惜佢就令我好失望<br />\n成日藍剃 灰剃<br />\n或者過幾日先黎搵我<br />\n有時我type好長一段野比佢<br />\n但係佢都係好hea咁覆左幾個emoji算<br />\n不過我又見佢得閒up fb<br />\n或者同其他人係度comment緊<br />\n所以<br />\n其實佢係咪已經唔再鍾意我<br />\n或者說已經根本不在乎我"},{"pid":"e73fa69e937b56c95575533008722af006adf086","tid":875214,"uid":201604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-24T17:50:51.000Z","msg":"兵"},{"pid":"ff9aac326377af55e2bcf0a248ce59c2e6b6067a","tid":875214,"uid":2263,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-24T17:51:03.000Z","msg":"係"},{"pid":"1796c9817fe91bd59eb69730595b4baafcdb20d0","tid":875214,"uid":218450,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e73fa69e937b56c95575533008722af006adf086","tid":875214,"uid":201604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-24T17:50:51.000Z","msg":"兵"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-24T17:52:07.000Z","msg":"咁可以點算<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6488d44337f872a5e96b0df07e8b472030021c55","tid":875214,"uid":173326,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-24T17:52:25.000Z","msg":"藍剔返佢"},{"pid":"f5e256e7062f815a123213c31ae4446dc127c248","tid":875214,"uid":21423,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-24T17:52:51.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d54112b7e182f856a80fccb20961733bc89f1634","tid":875214,"uid":218450,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6488d44337f872a5e96b0df07e8b472030021c55","tid":875214,"uid":173326,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTi